about.summary: Many models contain tuning parameters (i.e. parameters that cannot be directly estimated from the data). These tools can be used to define objects for creating, simulating, or validating values for such parameters.

name: r-dials
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.0.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-dials
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/dials_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/dials/dials_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b06031964d84d3aabf11fd8e65f50e38ace88c6136321f25908c8e247683e8c6

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1001
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr
    - r-glue
    - r-purrr
    - r-rlang
    - r-scales
    - r-tibble
    - r-withr
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr
    - r-glue
    - r-purrr
    - r-rlang
    - r-scales
    - r-tibble
    - r-withr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('dials')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('dials')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://tidymodels.github.io/dials
  license: GPL-2
  summary: 'Many models contain tuning parameters (i.e. parameters that cannot be directly estimated
    from the data). These tools can be used to define objects for creating, simulating,
    or validating values for such parameters. '
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
    - philip-khor
